00:35:50,122 --> 00:35:52,540
He said Martin flipped over it.

487
00:35:52,708 --> 00:35:54,375
Martin's known for his flipping.

488
00:35:54,543 --> 00:35:58,296
When it's time to make a deal,
he flips out.

489
00:35:58,464 --> 00:36:03,551
Why don't I pick you up a script,
then you can read it yourself?

490
00:36:04,803 --> 00:36:06,220
Don't go out of your way.

491
