496
00:36:24,239 --> 00:36:26,324
That's all right. Another time.

497
00:36:28,952 --> 00:36:30,036
See you round.

498
00:36:32,915 --> 00:36:34,040
See you.

499
00:36:35,209 --> 00:36:37,752
(music playing on stereo)

500
00:36:56,730 --> 00:37:00,942
Hi. My name is Ray,
I'm a friend of Chili Palmer's.

501
00:37:02,319 --> 00:37:04,779
Have you spoken with Mr. Palmer
since your husband blew up?

502
00:37:05,864 --> 00:37:07,615
Oh, once or twice.

503
00:37:07,783 --> 00:37:09,325
What was it you talked about?

504
00:37:09,493 --> 00:37:11,661
Nothing really. This and that.

505
00:37:11,829 --> 00:37:13,121
This and that?

506
00:37:15,958 --> 00:37:20,962
Fay... Fay, I want us
to be friends, I really do.

507
00:37:21,130 --> 00:37:26,134
And we all know friends don't hit
each other unless they have to.

508
00:37:26,301 --> 00:37:32,014
So what do you say you tell me
exactly what the fuck is goin' on?

509
00:37:32,182 --> 00:37:33,558
(sobs)

510
00:37:33,726 --> 00:37:35,101
OK?

511
00:37:40,774 --> 00:37:42,191
Good evening, sir.

512
00:37:42,359 --> 00:37:44,736
And a very good evening
to you too, sir.

513
00:38:09,094 --> 00:38:10,094
Leo.

514
00:38:11,013 --> 00:38:12,180
Look at me.

515
00:38:15,684 --> 00:38:20,062
I'd have never thought you'd be so dumb.
Leaving over 300 grand in a closet.

516
00:38:21,190 --> 00:38:22,523
I guess you are.

517
00:38:23,275 --> 00:38:27,111
I didn't know where else to keep it.
Where would you?

518
00:38:27,279 --> 00:38:28,696
How 'bout a bank?

519
00:38:28,864 --> 00:38:31,240
They'd report it to the IRS.

520
00:38:31,408 --> 00:38:36,162
You don't open an account,
you get a safe deposit box.

521
00:38:36,330 --> 00:38:38,164
How did you know I was here?

522
00:38:39,541 --> 00:38:42,543
Next time you write to your wife,
don't use hotel stationery.

523
00:38:42,711 --> 00:38:44,545
It was Fay, wasn't it?

524
00:38:44,713 --> 00:38:47,048
Did she tell you my life history?

525
00:38:47,216 --> 00:38:49,717
Leo, I'm here to save your ass.

526
00:38:49,885 --> 00:38:52,345
How? By taking my money?

527
00:38:52,513 --> 00:38:54,514
No, the money you won today is yours.

528
00:38:54,681 --> 00:38:55,932
It's all mine!

529
00:38:56,099 --> 00:38:57,767
Leo, sit down.

530
00:39:01,188 --> 00:39:04,482
I don't know how you got this far,
you're so fuckin' dumb,

531
00:39:04,650 --> 00:39:07,193
but you're through,
and I'll explain why.

532
00:39:09,571 --> 00:39:12,031
Ray Bones is the man
you're dealing with now,

533
00:39:12,199 --> 00:39:17,829
and when he finds out what you did,
he'll take everything.

534
00:39:17,996 --> 00:39:20,623
Then most likely he'll shoot you,
so you won't tell.

535
00:39:21,750 --> 00:39:24,252
I'm not gonna do that.
I'm not gonna hurt you.

536
00:39:24,419 --> 00:39:29,632
There's 310,000 here. I'm taking the
300 you scammed from the airlines,

537
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:33,427
and the ten that's over,
I'm gonna borrow from you.

538
00:39:34,388 --> 00:39:38,850
Wait... You take all my money,
but you're borrowing part of it?

539
00:39:39,017 --> 00:39:42,520
At 18%. Don't ask another
fuckin' question. I'm leaving now.

540
00:39:46,108 --> 00:39:49,610
