in your story is critical.

1263
01:27:37,268 --> 01:27:42,021
This shouldn't be a hop in the sack.
These two should fall in love.

1264
01:27:42,189 --> 01:27:43,481
Which two?

1265
01:27:43,649 --> 01:27:47,235
Then, when the mob guy's
chasing them,

1266
01:27:47,403 --> 01:27:51,156
it adds a wistful element
to their romance.

1267
01:27:51,323 --> 01:27:52,782
Mob guy?

1268
01:27:52,950 --> 01:27:56,745
As the mob guy, it's another
man's wife I'm sleeping with.

1269
01:27:56,912 --> 01:27:58,997
After all, you have such morals.

1270
01:28:01,250 --> 01:28:06,880
I have to run, but I'd like to see
them having misgivings

1271
01:28:07,047 --> 01:28:10,300
about wanting the money.
It's a moral dilemma for them.

1272
01:28:10,468 --> 01:28:14,012
They rationalize taking it,
but in the end, they can't.

1273
01:28:14,180 --> 01:28:17,182
- What money?
- The 300 large.

1274
01:28:17,349 --> 01:28:19,601
