1276
01:28:22,897 --> 01:28:24,063
I am that shylock.

1277
01:28:27,985 --> 01:28:29,652
Look at me, Harry.

1278
01:28:31,238 --> 01:28:34,032
(Chili) Not bad!
You're really getting it down.

1279
01:28:34,200 --> 01:28:38,578
It scares me how well I know this guy.
I could do this tomorrow.

1280
01:28:43,250 --> 01:28:48,880
Doll face. You should think
about getting back into acting.

1281
01:28:49,048 --> 01:28:51,883
- I'll give it some heavy thought.
- OK.

1282
01:28:57,223 --> 01:28:58,848
Take care of yourself, Harry.

1283
01:29:03,729 --> 01:29:04,896
Enjoy.

1284
